description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, styling, and the main App component. It creates the root DOM element and renders the App component inside a StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root to manage rendering of React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root DOM element.
